parameters: --\c[17]【Drum of Full Revival】\c[0] has been obtained!

Oh! All three of you fell into the hole quite spectacularly,
but is everyone unharmed?
Master! You came to search for us underground?

Now all four of us are together. I was worried when we got
separated because of the pitfall, but I'm glad we could
safely regroup.

...By the way, did you encounter any strange enemies on your
way here? Like a monster with wriggling tentacles?
触手　結果　花梨

Ah, those disgusting tentacles? They were blocking the path
on the way here, so I slashed them in two! (Hmph!)
触手　結果　花梨
触手　結果　花梨

...I was caught off guard and restrained for a bit, but
afterwards, I tore them to pieces.
触手　結果　夕霧

They were annoying enemies trying to restrain us, so I
chopped them up so they'll never attack anyone again.
触手　結果　夕霧
触手　結果　夕霧

...I let my guard down and got restrained, it was tough... I
never want to fight that enemy again...
触手　結果　紅葉

Those tentacles were indeed bothersome. But I managed to
defeat them without being harmed.
触手　結果　紅葉
触手　結果　紅葉

...Hmm, it was quite a challenging enemy. Despite various
things happening, it's good that we were able to regroup
safely.
触手　結果　真沙妃

I see. No, it was an unnecessary question. Well, let's not
dawdle. Let's hurry on ahead.
触手　結果　真沙妃
触手　結果　真沙妃
The shaking is getting stronger and stronger!
We must hurry to Mount Fuji to stop the Gyōon ritual!

Indeed. We don't have time to waste in a place like this.
The exit is just ahead. Let's hurry, Karin--!
Yes! Let's all head to the surface!
--Karin and the others headed for the exit!
I wonder where everyone is... I should wait here...

Tsk...! To be caught in such a pitfall, as a ninja, this
is a blunder--!

...Being alone means the others must have fallen somewhere
else? It's dangerous to be alone in enemy territory. I need
to hurry and regroup with Karin and the others.
Are we near the surface yet?
Karin!? Good, it seems you're safe.

Yeah. We really got dropped into a troublesome spot, huh? I
wonder if Momiji-san and Masaki-chan are okay?

I'm not sure. It would be bad if we moved on ahead and
couldn't regroup with them. Let's wait here for a while for
the two of them.
Right. I hope they're both safe.

Ouch... It hurts... Looks like I was knocked out for a
while...

This hole doesn't look climbable. There must be an exit
somewhere. I need to regroup with Karin-chan and the others
quickly--
Thank goodness! Momiji-san is safe too!
Where is Masaki-dono? Wasn't she with you, Momiji-dono?

Perhaps... our master might not have fallen into the hole.
But surely, she will come looking for us.

We shouldn't move around strangely until all four of us are
together. We'll wait here for Masaki-dono, Karin. Is that
alright?

Hmm... Have the three of you still not managed to climb up
here?
It can't be helped. Shall I go to meet them?
